snippet.title: Masters of Madness (Cthulhu Idle Clicker) - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
🐙 DOWNLOAD HERE 🐙
Android PlayStore: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.antiway.mastersofmadness

Masters of Madness is an idle game / clicker where you can tap manually or engage different minions to collect souls for you. Collect souls, cast sigils, and summon Cthulhu! With each ascension you'll meet the Lovecraftian Outer Gods and acquire their Blessings for even stronger runs! 

◆ Like the Official Masters of Madness Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/mastersofmadnessgame/
◆ Join other Cthulhu Acolytes on Reddit:
https://www.reddit.com/r/mastersofmadness/
◆ Follow us on Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/antiwaystudios/
